text: Desmiphora pallida is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Bates in 1874. It is known from Brazil, Bolivia, Jamaica and Peru.BioLib.cz - Desmiphora pallida. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Desmiphora Category:Beetles described in 1874
title: Desmiphora pallida
